    <para id="id7309116">ECONOMIC AND MANAGEMENT SCIENCES</para>
    <para id="id7309120">Grade 4</para>
    <para id="id7309125">THE CORNER CAFÉ</para>
    <para id="id7309129">Module 5</para>
    <para id="id7309134">HOW THE CAFÉ IS RUN</para>
    <para id="id7309138">Let’s go and take a look at the corner café.</para>
    <list id="id7309144" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
      <item>Business premises</item>
    </list>
    <para id="id7309153">Have you ever wondered why the owner actually decided to open a café right in the middle of a residential area?</para>
