      <para id="id7310196">Many of the activities of a café also take place “behind the scenes.” Do ask the manager if he could make it possible for you to visit the cold storage room and other storage areas as part of your research project.</para>
      <para id="id7310205">Assessment</para>
      <para id="id7310210">LEARNING OUTCOME 1: THE ECONOMIC CYCLE</para>
      <para id="id7310214">The learner will be able to demonstrate knowledge and understanding of the economic cycle within the context of “the economic problem”.</para>
